    public class AgitatorIdle
extends edu.wpi.first.wpilibj.command.Command
    Spins the ball agitator to prevent balls from getting stuck

    Note: This is the default command of Robot.agitator

        protected void initialize()
        This changes the setpoint of the ball agitator to the idle speed using RobotMap.AGITATOR_IDLE_SETPOINT

        Note: The agitator's PID loop is enables in Robot.robotInit(), so it doesn't need to be enabled here
